  "text": "In [CITATION_1] , the authors presented an analysis of topic modeling in the field of software engineering in order to specify the extent to which topic modeling had been applied to one or more software repositories. They focused on 167 articles written between December 1999 and December 2014 and evaluated the use of topic modeling in the area of software engineering. They identified and demonstrated research trends in mining unstructured repositories through topical modeling. They found that most studies focused only on a limited number of software engineering tasks.",
